This pool pays out using a proportional share reward system (your shares / total shares for the round) = % share of the rewards.

The service was first available on July 22nd, 2011.

##Features

* TXT/SMS idle miners notification (US numbers only)
* Built on redundant clustered systems, all servers are in a cluster, even the firewall and load balancer.
* Offers managed rig OS (Linux) that features an iPhone/Mobile internet page. You can update and check on your rig from your cell phone. Enables easy overclocking and monitors itself for heat problems.

##Reward distribution

* Proportional: 3% fee.

